  "corner": "screen_english",
  "corner_label": "Screen English",
  "title": "",
  "movie": "미스비헤이비어 (Misbehaviour)",
  "duration_sec": 704.02,
  "audio_url": "https://rtyzdyyfahddqshgyjvn.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/gmp-audio/2020-07-23_screen_english.mp3",
  "script": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 1.42,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬"
    },
    {
      "start": 1.42,
      "end": 20.96,
      "text": "영화를 즐기는 또 하나의 아이디어"
    },
    {
      "start": 20.96,
      "end": 22.84,
      "text": "스크린 잉글리쉬 타임"
    },
    {
      "start": 22.84,
      "end": 24.78,
      "text": "7월에 함께 하고 있는 영화는"
    },
    {
      "start": 24.78,
      "end": 26.48,
      "text": "필리파 로 towelp 감독의"
    },
    {
      "start": 27.16,
      "end": 28.38,
      "text": "Miss Behavior"
    },
    {
      "start": 28.38,
      "end": 30.68,
      "text": "와우 하이 그리셉"
    },
    {
      "start": 30.68,
      "end": 31.38,
      "text": "와하우"
    },
    {
      "start": 31.38,
      "end": 32.0,
      "text": "Good morning"
    },
    {
      "start": 32.0,
      "end": 35.34,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.34,
      "end": 35.46,
      "text": "네"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.46,
      "end": 37.0,
      "text": "기분 좋게 시작을 하게 됩니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 37.5,
      "end": 39.5,
      "text": "우리가 영화를 보면요"
    },
    {
      "start": 40.16,
      "end": 43.72,
      "text": "주인공 Sally에게 딸이 있잖아요"
    },
    {
      "start": 44.02,
      "end": 44.42,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.6,
      "end": 46.6,
      "text": "I remember her voice saying like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 46.9,
      "end": 48.42,
      "text": "I'm a Miss World Lady."
    },
    {
      "start": 49.38,
      "end": 50.66,
      "text": "안 비슷해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.46,
      "end": 52.6,
      "text": "She was dressing up."
    },
    {
      "start": 52.72,
      "end": 53.44,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 53.66,
      "end": 54.22,
      "text": "괜찮았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 54.54,
      "end": 55.14,
      "text": "괜찮았어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.22,
      "end": 55.62,
      "text": "감사합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 55.96,
      "end": 56.68,
      "text": "It was very cute."
    },
    {
      "start": 56.78,
      "end": 56.9,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 57.76,
      "end": 59.4,
      "text": "Not as cute as this girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.58,
      "end": 60.02,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 60.16,
      "end": 61.0,
      "text": "따라갈 수가 없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 61.16,
      "end": 63.48,
      "text": "이 어린 소녀의 목소리는 따라할 수가 없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 63.7,
      "end": 64.4,
      "text": "Yeah, of course."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.54,
      "end": 64.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 65.12,
      "end": 69.76,
      "text": "Anyway, her name was Abigail Thaw라는 이름을 갖고 있더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 70.0,
      "end": 71.16,
      "text": "Abigail Thaw."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.16,
      "end": 74.54,
      "text": "Yeah, 근데 찾아보니까 배우가 되었더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.9,
      "end": 76.26,
      "text": "Yeah, she became an actress."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.64,
      "end": 76.74,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.94,
      "end": 80.24,
      "text": "She has acted in many, many plays, musicals."
    },
    {
      "start": 80.24,
      "end": 82.84,
      "text": "She was part of a musical troupe."
    },
    {
      "start": 82.92,
      "end": 84.04,
      "text": "Whoa, very talented."
    },
    {
      "start": 84.54,
      "end": 87.74,
      "text": "And also her dad, not Sally's boyfriend,"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.04,
      "end": 91.54,
      "text": "but her real dad, the one she divorced from,"
    },
    {
      "start": 91.94,
      "end": 93.82,
      "text": "he was also an actor."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.02,
      "end": 95.72,
      "text": "A pretty well-known actor."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.86,
      "end": 96.7,
      "text": "I looked him up."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.84,
      "end": 97.66,
      "text": "Very handsome."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.9,
      "end": 99.92,
      "text": "He passed away a while back."
    },
    {
      "start": 99.92,
      "end": 102.34,
      "text": "But I think I've seen him before."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.34,
      "end": 107.52,
      "text": "아, 친아빠가 이제 John Thaw라고 하는 배우였다고 하는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 108.72,
      "end": 111.02,
      "text": "제가 생각하기에는, is it the power of genes?"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.72,
      "end": 113.04,
      "text": "It runs in the family."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.14,
      "end": 113.68,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 113.7,
      "end": 114.94,
      "text": "이럴 때 항상 하는 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 115.04,
      "end": 116.2,
      "text": "It runs in the family."
    },
    {
      "start": 116.54,
      "end": 116.84,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 117.28,
      "end": 118.72,
      "text": "It runs in the family."
    },
    {
      "start": 118.84,
      "end": 119.16,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 119.48,
      "end": 122.9,
      "text": "정말 이 유전자의 power 무시할 수가 없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 122.9,
      "end": 124.74,
      "text": "Her mom also, by the way,"
    },
    {
      "start": 125.16,
      "end": 126.66,
      "text": "she got her acting from her dad,"
    },
    {
      "start": 126.94,
      "end": 130.72,
      "text": "and she got her strong spirit from her mom, partially."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.06,
      "end": 131.24,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 131.5,
      "end": 132.08,
      "text": "She said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 132.32,
      "end": 135.7,
      "text": "I was always brought up to believe I was equal to a man."
    },
    {
      "start": 135.82,
      "end": 136.24,
      "text": "Oh."
    },
    {
      "start": 137.31,
      "end": 138.61,
      "text": "It was a simple doctrine,"
    },
    {
      "start": 139.11,
      "end": 141.15,
      "text": "and my mom taught me how to do this."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.23,
      "end": 141.53,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 141.69,
      "end": 145.35,
      "text": "So she received a lot of strength from her mom,"
    },
    {
      "start": 145.47,
      "end": 148.13,
      "text": "being such an active lady and a feminist."
    },
    {
      "start": 148.13,
      "end": 148.85,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 149.07,
      "end": 153.83,
      "text": "지금 이 Abigail, 그러니까 Sally의 딸이 한 이야기를 들려주셨는데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 154.35,
      "end": 156.57,
      "text": "확실히 she grew up with a good education."
    },
    {
      "start": 156.93,
      "end": 157.25,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 157.47,
      "end": 161.27,
      "text": "엄마가 여성 운동을 했던 사람이라 그런지,"
    },
    {
      "start": 161.51,
      "end": 165.47,
      "text": "딸도 남성이든 여성이든 인권, 평등함,"
    },
    {
      "start": 165.61,
      "end": 168.85,
      "text": "이런 것에 대해서 많이 배우고 자란 사람이 되었나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.05,
      "end": 169.25,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 169.51,
      "end": 171.41,
      "text": "So I found her pictures on the internet."
    },
    {
      "start": 171.83,
      "end": 172.45,
      "text": "Oh, the daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 172.59,
      "end": 173.03,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 173.25,
      "end": 174.09,
      "text": "Abigail Thaw."
    },
    {
      "start": 174.09,
      "end": 175.09,
      "text": "Oh, 그랬더니요."
    },
    {
      "start": 175.17,
      "end": 178.53,
      "text": "왠지 모르게 조금 당당한 그런 느낌이 막 들더라고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 178.89,
      "end": 182.31,
      "text": "Maybe I saw her with some preconceived notions."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.63,
      "end": 182.95,
      "text": "Uh-huh."
    },
    {
      "start": 182.97,
      "end": 183.33,
      "text": "그쵸?"
    },
    {
      "start": 183.41,
      "end": 184.53,
      "text": "She looked strong."
    },
    {
      "start": 184.75,
      "end": 186.95,
      "text": "Oh, 굉장히 당당해 보였어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 187.01,
      "end": 188.75,
      "text": "Like she had big shoulders."
    },
    {
      "start": 188.95,
      "end": 189.97,
      "text": "Oh, 그런 건 아니지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 190.03,
      "end": 190.85,
      "text": "She had her chin up."
    },
    {
      "start": 191.35,
      "end": 192.95,
      "text": "약간 chin up은 되어 있었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 192.97,
      "end": 193.59,
      "text": "She held her chin up."
    },
    {
      "start": 193.67,
      "end": 196.05,
      "text": "Oh, 약간 연기한 장면이었던 것 같기도 한데,"
    },
    {
      "start": 196.15,
      "end": 199.71,
      "text": "굉장히 뭔가 당당한 포스, 아우라가 느껴졌습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 199.81,
      "end": 201.43,
      "text": "She was always encouraged to speak up."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.49,
      "end": 201.73,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 201.73,
      "end": 205.21,
      "text": "And she felt that there was, whenever there was an injustice,"
    },
    {
      "start": 205.65,
      "end": 208.17,
      "text": "she would stand strong against injustice."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.39,
      "end": 208.51,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 208.73,
      "end": 209.95,
      "text": "So yeah, I can see that."
    },
    {
      "start": 209.97,
      "end": 210.73,
      "text": "그래서 그럴 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 210.75,
      "end": 211.71,
      "text": "당당했을 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 211.85,
      "end": 211.93,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 212.35,
      "end": 213.83,
      "text": "자, 오늘 장면 기대해 주세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 214.74,
      "end": 217.82,
      "text": "Do you know what really makes me laugh about all this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 218.48,
      "end": 222.56,
      "text": "You fighting for women's rights when you always took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 223.04,
      "end": 226.04,
      "text": "When I grow up, I want to be like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 226.42,
      "end": 228.04,
      "text": "That's because he did things."
    },
    {
      "start": 228.04,
      "end": 231.48,
      "text": "He smoked cigarettes and went in taxis and had adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 231.62,
      "end": 232.8,
      "text": "I wanted to have adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 233.99,
      "end": 239.31,
      "text": "Oh, 이번 장면에는 샐리의 어머니인 에블린이 등장을 하는데요."
    },
    {
      "start": 239.83,
      "end": 242.15,
      "text": "She didn't like what her daughter did."
    },
    {
      "start": 242.33,
      "end": 242.73,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 243.19,
      "end": 246.81,
      "text": "And her daughter, I guess she had more respect for her dad."
    },
    {
      "start": 246.95,
      "end": 250.23,
      "text": "This is a very interesting mother-daughter relationship."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.49,
      "end": 250.93,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 250.93,
      "end": 253.95,
      "text": "원래 딸들이 아빠를 그렇게 좋아하나요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 254.07,
      "end": 254.75,
      "text": "절대요."
    },
    {
      "start": 255.33,
      "end": 256.91,
      "text": "In my house, it's the complete opposite."
    },
    {
      "start": 257.15,
      "end": 257.99,
      "text": "경험담, 그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 259.19,
      "end": 260.81,
      "text": "Daddy, 저리 가."
    },
    {
      "start": 260.95,
      "end": 261.55,
      "text": "아, 그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 261.73,
      "end": 262.07,
      "text": "엄마."
    },
    {
      "start": 262.43,
      "end": 263.43,
      "text": "어머나 세상에."
    },
    {
      "start": 263.51,
      "end": 264.57,
      "text": "I hear that every day."
    },
    {
      "start": 264.71,
      "end": 265.11,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 265.55,
      "end": 270.57,
      "text": "이게 우리가 얼만큼 나이가 드느냐 아니면 나이가 어리냐에 상관없이"
    },
    {
      "start": 270.57,
      "end": 274.73,
      "text": "엄마하고 딸 사이는 원래 굉장히 특별합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.25,
      "end": 275.55,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 275.65,
      "end": 276.83,
      "text": "저의 경우도 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 277.01,
      "end": 277.43,
      "text": "How about you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 277.43,
      "end": 283.29,
      "text": "Oh, I often, not sometimes, act like a child in front of my mom."
    },
    {
      "start": 283.79,
      "end": 284.43,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 285.07,
      "end": 291.15,
      "text": "짜증도 막 내고 그러면서 막 친구같이 수다도 떨고 그러다가 뭐 슬픈 일 있으면"
    },
    {
      "start": 291.15,
      "end": 296.19,
      "text": "막 엉엉 울다가 다시 화도 냈다가 그러다가 또 우리 엄마 내가 챙겨야지"
    },
    {
      "start": 296.19,
      "end": 298.55,
      "text": "막 이러면서 챙겨도 주다가 이러네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 298.89,
      "end": 301.01,
      "text": "And does your mom appreciate you?"
    },
    {
      "start": 301.23,
      "end": 302.03,
      "text": "Yeah, I think so."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.33,
      "end": 302.95,
      "text": "That's good."
    },
    {
      "start": 302.95,
      "end": 303.45,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 303.45,
      "end": 308.47,
      "text": "일단은 오늘 대화를 잘 이해하기 위해서 우리 세 가지 표현 미리 알아보려고 해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 309.41,
      "end": 311.19,
      "text": "Took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 311.37,
      "end": 311.61,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 312.01,
      "end": 314.01,
      "text": "Took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 314.37,
      "end": 317.25,
      "text": "This is what I wish would happen in my house."
    },
    {
      "start": 317.43,
      "end": 318.43,
      "text": "네, 그러실 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 318.45,
      "end": 320.15,
      "text": "Why don't you take your father's side?"
    },
    {
      "start": 320.43,
      "end": 323.81,
      "text": "이 얘기 오늘 댁에 가셔서 활용해 보시면 좋을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 323.97,
      "end": 324.29,
      "text": "아, 예."
    },
    {
      "start": 324.41,
      "end": 324.59,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 324.79,
      "end": 325.43,
      "text": "사모가겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 325.43,
      "end": 330.81,
      "text": "네, 여기서 take one's side라는 것을 딱 뽑아다가 정리를 하면 좋을 것 같은데"
    },
    {
      "start": 330.81,
      "end": 334.29,
      "text": "두둔하다 혹은 변호하다라는 의미입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 334.45,
      "end": 341.53,
      "text": "그래서 took your father's side라고 했으니까 항상 아버지 편에 섰다라고 해석하실 수 있는 표현이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 341.57,
      "end": 343.23,
      "text": "Whose side are you going to take?"
    },
    {
      "start": 343.67,
      "end": 345.29,
      "text": "Daddy's side or mommy's side?"
    },
    {
      "start": 345.29,
      "end": 347.41,
      "text": "Mommy's side가 되겠죠, 저희 경우도."
    },
    {
      "start": 347.59,
      "end": 347.89,
      "text": "No."
    },
    {
      "start": 348.29,
      "end": 349.07,
      "text": "Sorry, Daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 349.49,
      "end": 350.53,
      "text": "Please come here."
    },
    {
      "start": 351.97,
      "end": 352.75,
      "text": "아, 예."
    },
    {
      "start": 352.85,
      "end": 353.59,
      "text": "그럴 수밖에 없어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 353.71,
      "end": 354.73,
      "text": "아유, 기분 업 시키세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 354.81,
      "end": 355.77,
      "text": "너무 슬퍼하지 마세요."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.03,
      "end": 357.67,
      "text": "Grow up."
    },
    {
      "start": 357.73,
      "end": 359.07,
      "text": "예, 업 시켰습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 359.15,
      "end": 359.55,
      "text": "Grow up."
    },
    {
      "start": 359.57,
      "end": 360.19,
      "text": "Grow up."
    },
    {
      "start": 360.43,
      "end": 362.95,
      "text": "성장하다, 철들다 라는 의미죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 363.29,
      "end": 364.19,
      "text": "Yeah, grow up."
    },
    {
      "start": 364.27,
      "end": 365.33,
      "text": "철들어."
    },
    {
      "start": 366.23,
      "end": 366.79,
      "text": "Adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 367.79,
      "end": 372.87,
      "text": "Adventures라고 하면 모험, 모험심이라고 해석이 되는 단어입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 373.39,
      "end": 375.11,
      "text": "Yeah, adventure, grow up."
    },
    {
      "start": 375.45,
      "end": 376.61,
      "text": "Took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 376.75,
      "end": 380.19,
      "text": "이 세 가지 표현들 더 집중해서 쩡긋 해보시는 거 잊지 마시고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 380.51,
      "end": 381.57,
      "text": "내용 다시 한번 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 381.57,
      "end": 385.53,
      "text": "Do you know what really makes me laugh about all this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 386.25,
      "end": 390.27,
      "text": "You fighting for women's rights when you always took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 390.85,
      "end": 393.77,
      "text": "When I grow up, I want to be like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 394.15,
      "end": 395.75,
      "text": "That's because he did things."
    },
    {
      "start": 395.93,
      "end": 399.15,
      "text": "He smoked cigarettes and went in taxis and had adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 399.33,
      "end": 400.49,
      "text": "I wanted to have adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 400.49,
      "end": 407.04,
      "text": "Both are quarreling, arguing, or disputing."
    },
    {
      "start": 407.24,
      "end": 408.54,
      "text": "Yeah, it's an argument."
    },
    {
      "start": 408.84,
      "end": 409.14,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 409.4,
      "end": 411.24,
      "text": "And not very typical argument."
    },
    {
      "start": 411.5,
      "end": 411.82,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 412.12,
      "end": 413.6,
      "text": "I'm jealous."
    },
    {
      "start": 414.16,
      "end": 416.24,
      "text": "Sally was such a daddy's girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 416.24,
      "end": 416.98,
      "text": "Oh, 그러네요."
    },
    {
      "start": 417.08,
      "end": 419.06,
      "text": "She was so in love with her daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 419.1,
      "end": 419.76,
      "text": "Oh, 굉장히 유니크해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 419.76,
      "end": 421.34,
      "text": "And she wanted to do everything with him."
    },
    {
      "start": 421.34,
      "end": 425.14,
      "text": "Yeah, 진짜 유니크한 그런 personality를 가지고 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 425.56,
      "end": 432.06,
      "text": "지금 Sally하고 Sally 엄마와의 대화인데 아주 태격, 태격하고 있는 그런 흥미진진한 장면이었어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 432.06,
      "end": 433.56,
      "text": "자, 내용 알아볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 433.78,
      "end": 437.28,
      "text": "Do you know what really makes me laugh about all this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 437.28,
      "end": 442.08,
      "text": "네, 엄마가 약간 화, 울분에 차서 목소리가 이렇게 나옵니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 442.52,
      "end": 445.6,
      "text": "Do you know what really makes me laugh about all this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 445.7,
      "end": 448.14,
      "text": "Oh, you sound like an Italian gangster."
    },
    {
      "start": 448.86,
      "end": 450.52,
      "text": "아니, gangster까지."
    },
    {
      "start": 450.68,
      "end": 451.28,
      "text": "Mafia."
    },
    {
      "start": 451.52,
      "end": 452.3,
      "text": "아, 진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 452.42,
      "end": 453.06,
      "text": "Do you know?"
    },
    {
      "start": 453.26,
      "end": 456.46,
      "text": "와, 마피아 하니까 갑자기 시칠리아가 떠오릅니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 456.74,
      "end": 459.02,
      "text": "Ah, do you know what will happen?"
    },
    {
      "start": 459.02,
      "end": 462.5,
      "text": "저 시칠리아, I went there about seven years ago."
    },
    {
      "start": 462.66,
      "end": 463.32,
      "text": "Oh, nice."
    },
    {
      "start": 463.4,
      "end": 464.66,
      "text": "Yeah, 정말 좋았는데 말이죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 464.66,
      "end": 465.44,
      "text": "A little vacation."
    },
    {
      "start": 465.78,
      "end": 466.94,
      "text": "Italian vacation."
    },
    {
      "start": 467.1,
      "end": 467.78,
      "text": "그러게 말입니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 468.02,
      "end": 469.68,
      "text": "지금은 꿈같은 일이 되어버렸지만."
    },
    {
      "start": 469.98,
      "end": 470.42,
      "text": "자, 어쨌든."
    },
    {
      "start": 470.84,
      "end": 473.92,
      "text": "Do you know what really makes me laugh about all this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 474.44,
      "end": 475.32,
      "text": "너는, 어?"
    },
    {
      "start": 475.82,
      "end": 478.0,
      "text": "내가 웃게 되는 게 뭔지 알아?"
    },
    {
      "start": 478.26,
      "end": 478.6,
      "text": "라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 478.76,
      "end": 480.02,
      "text": "지금 제가 지금 흥분했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 480.5,
      "end": 482.34,
      "text": "진짜 웃는 게 너 뭔지 알아?"
    },
    {
      "start": 482.76,
      "end": 484.6,
      "text": "라고 화를 내고 있는 그런 상황이에요."
    },
    {
      "start": 484.66,
      "end": 486.26,
      "text": "진짜 excited 됐네."
    },
    {
      "start": 486.26,
      "end": 487.08,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 487.08,
      "end": 498.58,
      "text": "Yeah, 엄마가 여기에서 아주 흥분하셔가지고 문법성을 다 챙기지 않고 이야기하고 계십니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 498.96,
      "end": 501.36,
      "text": "You fighting for women's rights."
    },
    {
      "start": 501.7,
      "end": 502.18,
      "text": "라고 했거든요."
    },
    {
      "start": 502.66,
      "end": 503.56,
      "text": "그러니까 원래는"
    },
    {
      "start": 503.56,
      "end": 506.1,
      "text": "You said you're fighting for women's rights."
    },
    {
      "start": 506.22,
      "end": 506.86,
      "text": "이게 맞겠죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 507.26,
      "end": 508.92,
      "text": "You fighting for women's rights."
    },
    {
      "start": 508.94,
      "end": 509.52,
      "text": "Yeah, 이렇게."
    },
    {
      "start": 509.68,
      "end": 511.0,
      "text": "이 현재 상황 얘기하는 거죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 511.18,
      "end": 511.32,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 511.54,
      "end": 513.9,
      "text": "네, 줄여가지고 이렇게 이야기를 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 513.9,
      "end": 517.8,
      "text": "너는 여성의 권리를 위해서 싸운다고 하지."
    },
    {
      "start": 518.5,
      "end": 521.48,
      "text": "When you always took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 522.08,
      "end": 522.92,
      "text": "이건 무슨 의미일까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 522.94,
      "end": 524.14,
      "text": "그 과거 상황이고."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.22,
      "end": 524.4,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 524.82,
      "end": 527.06,
      "text": "너는 항상 아버지 편에 있으면서 말이야."
    },
    {
      "start": 527.44,
      "end": 527.94,
      "text": "라는 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 528.02,
      "end": 530.64,
      "text": "When you were growing up, you were a daddy's girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 530.82,
      "end": 533.14,
      "text": "And now you're fighting for women's rights."
    },
    {
      "start": 533.3,
      "end": 533.42,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 533.62,
      "end": 534.52,
      "text": "Isn't it ironic?"
    },
    {
      "start": 534.98,
      "end": 536.62,
      "text": "내가 앞뒤가 안 맞지 않니?"
    },
    {
      "start": 536.72,
      "end": 537.14,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 537.14,
      "end": 538.66,
      "text": "It's this kind of argument."
    },
    {
      "start": 539.76,
      "end": 542.02,
      "text": "When I grow up, I want to be like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 542.22,
      "end": 543.14,
      "text": "이렇게 이야기했잖아."
    },
    {
      "start": 543.36,
      "end": 545.12,
      "text": "라고 하면서 인용도 해줍니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 545.64,
      "end": 547.98,
      "text": "When I grow up, I want to be like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 548.4,
      "end": 549.8,
      "text": "She's imitating her daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 549.9,
      "end": 550.26,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 550.32,
      "end": 551.36,
      "text": "In front of her daughter."
    },
    {
      "start": 551.5,
      "end": 551.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 552.06,
      "end": 553.82,
      "text": "지금 딸 앞에서 이렇게 따라하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 554.14,
      "end": 556.96,
      "text": "When I grow up, 내가 잘하면 I want to be like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 557.14,
      "end": 558.06,
      "text": "아빠처럼 될 거예요."
    },
    {
      "start": 558.6,
      "end": 559.64,
      "text": "Just what I want to hear."
    },
    {
      "start": 560.0,
      "end": 563.56,
      "text": "When I grow up, I want to marry someone like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 563.7,
      "end": 565.2,
      "text": "I hope your dreams come true."
    },
    {
      "start": 565.2,
      "end": 566.5,
      "text": "꿈만 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 566.5,
      "end": 567.06,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 568.98,
      "end": 571.98,
      "text": "Ah, that's because he did things."
    },
    {
      "start": 572.08,
      "end": 574.04,
      "text": "Oh, shell is contradicting her, right?"
    },
    {
      "start": 574.14,
      "end": 574.94,
      "text": "반박하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.16,
      "end": 575.52,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 575.8,
      "end": 577.98,
      "text": "That's because he did things."
    },
    {
      "start": 578.48,
      "end": 581.88,
      "text": "왜냐하면 아빠가 뭔가를 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 582.22,
      "end": 583.02,
      "text": "라고 이야기합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 583.48,
      "end": 585.2,
      "text": "I didn't do things."
    },
    {
      "start": 586.38,
      "end": 587.64,
      "text": "He smoked cigarettes."
    },
    {
      "start": 588.5,
      "end": 589.48,
      "text": "예를 들고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 589.58,
      "end": 591.46,
      "text": "좀 안 좋은 얘기 아닌가?"
    },
    {
      "start": 591.46,
      "end": 591.9,
      "text": "그게?"
    },
    {
      "start": 592.92,
      "end": 594.46,
      "text": "아빠가 담배도 폈고."
    },
    {
      "start": 594.46,
      "end": 599.2,
      "text": "And went in taxis and had adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 599.72,
      "end": 602.38,
      "text": "택시도 탔고, 모험도 했잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 602.82,
      "end": 603.96,
      "text": "뭐가 특별하죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 604.14,
      "end": 604.42,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 604.52,
      "end": 605.0,
      "text": "He smoked."
    },
    {
      "start": 605.12,
      "end": 605.94,
      "text": "He took taxis."
    },
    {
      "start": 606.34,
      "end": 607.5,
      "text": "Adventures 괜찮네."
    },
    {
      "start": 607.58,
      "end": 607.84,
      "text": "네."
    },
    {
      "start": 608.02,
      "end": 608.76,
      "text": "Had adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 609.42,
      "end": 611.7,
      "text": "I wanted to have adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 611.7,
      "end": 614.68,
      "text": "저도 모험이 하고 싶었다고요."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.88,
      "end": 616.78,
      "text": "라고 지금 반박을 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 617.78,
      "end": 618.58,
      "text": "당황했나 봐요."
    },
    {
      "start": 619.3,
      "end": 619.86,
      "text": "Mommy?"
    },
    {
      "start": 619.96,
      "end": 620.54,
      "text": "Can you imagine?"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.66,
      "end": 622.66,
      "text": "Mommy is feeling pretty heartbroken."
    },
    {
      "start": 622.92,
      "end": 623.26,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 623.66,
      "end": 625.64,
      "text": "Am I just a boring lady?"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.9,
      "end": 629.26,
      "text": "Did I do nothing to make you happy when you were growing up?"
    },
    {
      "start": 629.34,
      "end": 629.66,
      "text": "맞아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 629.92,
      "end": 633.86,
      "text": "딸이 이렇게 이야기를 하면 엄마의 입장에서는 굉장히 서운할 수도 있을 것 같아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 634.76,
      "end": 637.7,
      "text": "모녀의 대화 정말 참 흥미진진했습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 638.04,
      "end": 638.22,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 638.22,
      "end": 639.98,
      "text": "자, 이 내용 한 번 더 들어볼게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 640.22,
      "end": 643.92,
      "text": "Do you know what really makes me laugh about all this?"
    },
    {
      "start": 644.6,
      "end": 648.66,
      "text": "You fighting for women's rights when you always took your father's side."
    },
    {
      "start": 649.22,
      "end": 652.16,
      "text": "When I grow up, I want to be like daddy."
    },
    {
      "start": 652.54,
      "end": 654.12,
      "text": "That's because he did things."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.32,
      "end": 657.54,
      "text": "He smoked cigarettes and went in taxis and had adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 657.72,
      "end": 658.88,
      "text": "I wanted to have adventures."
    },
    {
      "start": 659.54,
      "end": 660.46,
      "text": "Cool."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.76,
      "end": 664.94,
      "text": "Let me tell you, the fighting between mother and daughter won't last long."
    },
    {
      "start": 664.94,
      "end": 666.16,
      "text": "Oh, it's over?"
    },
    {
      "start": 666.36,
      "end": 666.76,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 667.1,
      "end": 667.8,
      "text": "오래가지 않아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 667.9,
      "end": 669.04,
      "text": "엄마와 딸의 싸움은."
    },
    {
      "start": 669.16,
      "end": 670.82,
      "text": "It's like the 물빼기, 칼로."
    },
    {
      "start": 670.98,
      "end": 671.66,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 671.74,
      "end": 672.86,
      "text": "칼로 물빼기."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.02,
      "end": 673.16,
      "text": "그죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 673.36,
      "end": 675.68,
      "text": "그 다음 날 되면, 엄마 안녕!"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.92,
      "end": 676.48,
      "text": "또 이렇게 돼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 676.68,
      "end": 677.8,
      "text": "Oh, they make up right away?"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.96,
      "end": 678.28,
      "text": "Really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 678.4,
      "end": 678.94,
      "text": "완전히 잊어버려요."
    },
    {
      "start": 679.02,
      "end": 679.8,
      "text": "Is that how you do it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.82,
      "end": 680.74,
      "text": "네, 제가 딱 그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 681.0,
      "end": 681.96,
      "text": "You don't say sorry."
    },
    {
      "start": 682.1,
      "end": 683.88,
      "text": "Oh, I'm really sorry about last night."
    },
    {
      "start": 684.06,
      "end": 684.92,
      "text": "I didn't mean it."
    },
    {
      "start": 685.0,
      "end": 686.62,
      "text": "It depends on the situation."
    },
    {
      "start": 686.86,
      "end": 688.3,
      "text": "But yeah, sometimes I forget."
    },
    {
      "start": 688.3,
      "end": 691.0,
      "text": "아, 이 정도면 사과해야 되지 않을까."
    },
    {
      "start": 691.08,
      "end": 691.54,
      "text": "아, 그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 691.64,
      "end": 694.08,
      "text": "이 정도면 좀 그 다음날, 엄마, 내 맘 알지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.24,
      "end": 694.7,
      "text": "미안해."
    },
    {
      "start": 694.8,
      "end": 697.68,
      "text": "이 정도는 한번 이야기하고 넘어가야 되지 않을까 싶어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 697.82,
      "end": 698.2,
      "text": "쿨하게."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.38,
      "end": 698.62,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.94,
      "end": 701.06,
      "text": "자, 오늘 여기에서 마무리해볼까요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 701.48,
      "end": 701.96,
      "text": "All right."
    },
    {
      "start": 702.06,
      "end": 704.02,
      "text": "See you next Monday, Kreech."
    }
  ]
}